WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:25.400


00:01:31.590 --> 00:01:32.430
Nanny Zhou!

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:35.950
Why were you being unwilling?

00:01:36.310 --> 00:01:37.430
Didn't you hear that?

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.229
Mr. Liu is being

00:01:38.229 --> 00:01:39.789
promoted to Junior Vice Minister of Revenue.

00:01:40.070 --> 00:01:41.560
It's a third-rank official!

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:43.120
Such a good match

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.759
should be for my daughter Lan.

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:46.350
Why should Jinzhao take him!

00:01:46.870 --> 00:01:48.680
This match only appears good,

00:01:48.789 --> 00:01:49.950
nothing more.

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:50.870
How?

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:52.680
That Young Master Liu

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:53.870
is no good.

00:01:54.310 --> 00:01:55.150
Only eighteen,

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.310
he's already bedded

00:01:56.310 --> 00:01:57.789
several maids in his house.

00:01:58.950 --> 00:02:00.230
Any girl who marries him will

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:01.430
have nothing but hardship ahead.

00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:05.430
I may not have that much

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:06.950
bad blood with Jinzhao.

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:09.240
My dear Mistress!

00:02:09.430 --> 00:02:10.710
You're too kind!

00:02:11.430 --> 00:02:12.630
Jinzhao didn't go easy on you

00:02:12.710 --> 00:02:13.800
when she bullied you.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:15.280
Besides, Master

00:02:15.590 --> 00:02:17.240
only asked you to make the arrangements.

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:18.240
Whether she

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.030
actually marries into

00:02:19.150 --> 00:02:20.360
that family isn't your call.

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:22.360
It's up to Master and Madame.

00:02:22.710 --> 00:02:24.520
Why bother going against Master's wishes?

00:02:25.150 --> 00:02:26.280
Haven't you always wanted to

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.310
have leverage over Jinzhao?

00:02:28.150 --> 00:02:29.079
This marriage

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:30.590
is the best leverage.

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:32.870
Indeed.

00:02:36.240 --> 00:02:36.750
Alright,

00:02:37.310 --> 00:02:38.360
I'll take this task.

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:45.120
Miss,

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:46.800
as you instructed,

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:47.840
I've secretly checked

00:02:47.910 --> 00:02:49.190
everyone in our courtyard.

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:50.630
No holes

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:52.630
found yet.

00:02:53.710 --> 00:02:54.280
I'll check again

00:02:54.630 --> 00:02:55.470
the carriage house

00:02:55.470 --> 00:02:56.960
and the errand office.

00:02:57.430 --> 00:02:58.590
Everyone and everything

00:02:58.590 --> 00:03:00.030
that's had contact with us,

00:03:00.190 --> 00:03:00.910
I'll go it through.

00:03:01.750 --> 00:03:02.870
I know,

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:04.590
even if I

00:03:04.750 --> 00:03:06.080
find out that lurker,

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:07.800
I can't do much with them.

00:03:09.150 --> 00:03:10.080
But at least I'll know

00:03:10.310 --> 00:03:11.310
where we stand.

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:14.400
Here comes Lan!

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:21.520
Jinzhao!

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:24.360
Please have a seat.

00:03:27.470 --> 00:03:29.310
Someone just came to propose marriage for you!

00:03:29.910 --> 00:03:30.960
I was behind the screen

00:03:31.079 --> 00:03:32.430
when the matchmaker arrived,

00:03:32.710 --> 00:03:33.630
and when I heard

00:03:33.750 --> 00:03:35.360
it was for you,

00:03:35.430 --> 00:03:36.470
I rushed right over.

00:03:36.710 --> 00:03:38.520
They asked the matchmaker to send word

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:39.560
to the Liu family today.

00:03:39.910 --> 00:03:40.960
If the Liu find it suitable,

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:42.470
they'll deliver the birth-date betrothal slip!

00:03:46.190 --> 00:03:47.310
The Liu family

00:03:47.310 --> 00:03:48.560
is an old noble house,

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:50.630
having produced several Jinshi scholars.

00:03:51.079 --> 00:03:52.079
If Mr. Liu is promoted

00:03:52.079 --> 00:03:53.710
to Junior Vice Minister of Revenue,

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.360
that would be another step up.

00:03:55.710 --> 00:03:57.560
And Mrs. Liu

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:00.310
is the sister of the Changxing Marchioness.

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:02.590
What kind of person is the boy?

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:04.470
Since Master has chosen him,

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:06.030
he must be a good man.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:07.280
Am I right, Master?

00:04:08.430 --> 00:04:09.000
His father

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:11.000
and I have served together in the Revenue Ministry for years,

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:13.430
so we know each other well.

00:04:14.190 --> 00:04:16.000
I've never heard anything wrong

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:17.070
with that boy.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:19.630
Besides, he's also passed the preliminary exams.

00:04:19.829 --> 00:04:20.510
I hear he's even

00:04:20.870 --> 00:04:22.560
taken the autumn provincial exam this session.

00:04:23.430 --> 00:04:25.920
Busy studying for the exams,

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:27.240
his character

00:04:27.630 --> 00:04:28.920
can't be too bad.

00:04:30.830 --> 00:04:32.270
Sounds good enough.

00:04:34.070 --> 00:04:36.000
Jinzhao has already turned fifteen,

00:04:36.870 --> 00:04:38.750
so we should start looking into marriage prospects.

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:40.360
Jinzhao,

00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:41.720
what do you think?

00:04:42.600 --> 00:04:43.510
So,

00:04:44.159 --> 00:04:44.830
the matchmaker

00:04:45.159 --> 00:04:46.600
has already sent word to the Liu family?

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:48.040
Yes.

00:04:49.830 --> 00:04:50.430
Two families

00:04:50.430 --> 00:04:51.600
haven't met for the viewing.

00:04:52.159 --> 00:04:53.560
I don't even know what the young Liu

00:04:53.950 --> 00:04:55.000
looks like.

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:56.430
Why the rush?

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:57.870
As if I'm the one

00:04:57.870 --> 00:04:59.480
rushing to marry him.

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.310
That's right.

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.040
After all, we're the bride's family.

00:05:04.510 --> 00:05:05.870
What's noble being the bride's family?

00:05:06.950 --> 00:05:08.510
Jinzhao has just arrived in the capital

00:05:08.510 --> 00:05:09.480
and hadn't started socializing yet.

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:12.000
They don't know her at all.

00:05:12.270 --> 00:05:13.630
How could they come to propose first?

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:15.000
Besides,

00:05:15.630 --> 00:05:17.270
given the Liu family's status,

00:05:18.040 --> 00:05:20.000
what's wrong with lowering ourselves a bit?

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:21.480
The real benefit is what counts,

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:22.830
isn't it?

00:05:23.870 --> 00:05:24.800
Does my grandmother

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:26.270
know about this?

00:05:27.830 --> 00:05:29.070
I just found out myself

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:31.270
and haven't written to her.

00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:34.159
She raised me up.

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:35.750
If marriage is being arranged for me,

00:05:35.920 --> 00:05:37.070
she should have been told first.

00:05:38.430 --> 00:05:38.950
Right.

00:05:39.430 --> 00:05:41.680
She is far away in Tongzhou.

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:43.870
Once this matter takes shape,

00:05:44.159 --> 00:05:45.270
it's still soon enough

00:05:45.270 --> 00:05:46.430
to tell her.

00:05:54.390 --> 00:05:55.390
Are you

00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:56.510
deliberately

00:05:56.510 --> 00:05:57.600
keeping this from her?

00:05:58.830 --> 00:05:59.870
What are you talking about?

00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:02.600
Since ancient times,

00:06:03.430 --> 00:06:04.680
marriage is decided

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:06.950
by parents

00:06:06.950 --> 00:06:08.560
and matchmakers.

00:06:09.750 --> 00:06:10.720
Your grandmother

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:12.240
just needs to be informed.

00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:13.950
Whether she agrees

00:06:14.240 --> 00:06:15.310
or not,

00:06:15.510 --> 00:06:17.750
she doesn't get the final say.

00:06:19.310 --> 00:06:20.070
Oh really?

00:06:21.310 --> 00:06:22.560
But I heard that

00:06:22.750 --> 00:06:24.560
Grandmother strongly opposed it

00:06:24.920 --> 00:06:26.480
when my mother married you.

00:06:27.070 --> 00:06:29.120
Your own parents also disagreed.

00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:30.920
Yet you insisted

00:06:31.070 --> 00:06:32.510
on marrying anyway.

00:06:33.270 --> 00:06:34.159
Why didn't you

00:06:34.159 --> 00:06:35.680
obey your parents

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:36.800
back then?

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:38.680
You unfilial daughter!

00:06:38.830 --> 00:06:40.630
How dare you say such a thing?

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:41.830
Fine.

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:43.190
In any case, this matter

00:06:43.390 --> 00:06:44.720
must have Grandmother's consent,

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:46.070
otherwise, I won't agree.

00:06:46.430 --> 00:06:46.950
You!

00:06:47.800 --> 00:06:48.630
I'll take my leave now.

00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:55.070
Ma'am!

00:07:01.630 --> 00:07:02.750
I'll go check on

00:07:02.920 --> 00:07:04.480
the lunch preparations.

00:07:13.270 --> 00:07:13.720
See?

00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:16.240
This is your pampered daughter!

00:07:16.830 --> 00:07:17.680
I don't think

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:19.120
she's completely wrong.

00:07:20.310 --> 00:07:21.560
I should inform my mother first.

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:23.120
There's no rush.

00:07:23.630 --> 00:07:24.510
Besides,

00:07:24.950 --> 00:07:26.120
arranging a marriage for Jinzhao

00:07:26.430 --> 00:07:27.950
right after she came back

00:07:28.070 --> 00:07:29.310
is indeed too early.

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:31.160
Too early?

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:32.600
You've seen

00:07:33.159 --> 00:07:35.560
how she defies her elders.

00:07:38.159 --> 00:07:39.830
Making a scene at her coming-of-age ceremony

00:07:40.270 --> 00:07:41.600
was bad enough, but that's

00:07:41.600 --> 00:07:42.800
on your Ji family's turf.

00:07:43.390 --> 00:07:45.750
The Lin's birthday banquet was such a formal occasion,

00:07:46.190 --> 00:07:48.510
and she dared to openly talk back to me in front of everyone!

00:07:50.270 --> 00:07:52.270
Which family with a son

00:07:52.270 --> 00:07:53.390
would want to

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:54.800
marry her after that?

00:07:56.430 --> 00:07:57.190
I tell you,

00:07:57.190 --> 00:07:58.360
we must quickly arrange

00:07:58.920 --> 00:07:59.630
a match for her before

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:01.040
she causes even bigger trouble,

00:08:01.160 --> 00:08:02.870
then she really won't marry off at all!

00:08:07.950 --> 00:08:08.800
Talk some sense into her!

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.800
Why didn't you try to stop Master?

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:19.720
Enough about him.

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:23.160
This Young Master Liu.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:24.870
Master thinks highly of him,

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:26.870
but I still don't feel sure.

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:29.360
Have Luo Yongping

00:08:29.560 --> 00:08:30.630
go make some inquiries.

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:32.549
Yes, ma'am.

00:08:36.909 --> 00:08:39.080
You've never even met Liu Xiancheng.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:41.270
Why this refusal?

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:46.320
Is it because of

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:49.840
Mr. Ye Xian?

00:08:52.150 --> 00:08:53.550
What does that have to do with him?

00:08:55.630 --> 00:08:57.120
I'm just saying.

00:08:58.510 --> 00:08:59.390
Why does Father

00:08:59.390 --> 00:09:01.030
suddenly care about my marriage?

00:09:01.790 --> 00:09:02.720
This can't be

00:09:02.910 --> 00:09:04.120
that simple.

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:07.030
We need more information

00:09:07.030 --> 00:09:07.960
from outside.

00:09:09.750 --> 00:09:10.670
What are you doing?

00:09:11.270 --> 00:09:12.320
How dare you trespass

00:09:12.320 --> 00:09:13.270
on my Miss's grounds?

00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:18.960
What are you doing?

00:09:19.550 --> 00:09:20.510
Master has ordered

00:09:21.150 --> 00:09:22.720
that from today, Jinzhao should

00:09:23.030 --> 00:09:24.270
remain in the residence and

00:09:24.670 --> 00:09:25.720
may not leave

00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:26.870
without his consent.

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:28.240
He's going to ground me?

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:29.440
Miss,

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:31.270
he ordered us to

00:09:31.630 --> 00:09:32.910
keep you here no matter what.

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:34.150
Anyone who

00:09:34.150 --> 00:09:35.510
let you out without permission

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:36.720
will be beaten and then

00:09:36.840 --> 00:09:38.120
taken away by slave brokers.

00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:40.440
We're just following orders.

00:09:41.200 --> 00:09:43.030
We hope you won't take offense.

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:45.550
You old hag! I...

00:09:49.960 --> 00:09:51.630
Miss, why are you stopping me?

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:54.000
Is there any way you can help me get out of here?

00:10:04.910 --> 00:10:06.440
Thanks for your help.

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:08.630
But if Father

00:10:08.630 --> 00:10:09.960
finds out,

00:10:10.150 --> 00:10:11.270
will he punish you?

00:10:12.200 --> 00:10:13.150
It's okay.

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:14.200
He's never once

00:10:14.270 --> 00:10:14.790
blamed me

00:10:14.790 --> 00:10:16.120
since I was little.

00:10:17.150 --> 00:10:17.720
You can

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:18.510
take off

00:10:18.510 --> 00:10:19.550
Ziling's clothes later.

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:28.030
Take this.

00:10:29.390 --> 00:10:31.080
If this match goes through,

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:32.000
there'll be a great reward.

00:10:33.870 --> 00:10:34.360
By the way,

00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:36.150
when you

00:10:36.150 --> 00:10:37.320
see Mrs. Ji,

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:39.030
remember to tell her...

00:10:43.670 --> 00:10:44.480
Jinzhao,

00:10:44.670 --> 00:10:45.870
your new outfit

00:10:45.870 --> 00:10:46.870
is really beautiful.

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:48.360
What fabric is this?

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:49.870
If you like it,

00:10:50.030 --> 00:10:50.630
I'll buy you

00:10:50.630 --> 00:10:52.000
another bolt.

00:10:52.630 --> 00:10:54.240
Thank you, Jinzhao.

00:10:55.550 --> 00:10:56.080
Miss Jinzhao.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:57.270
Miss Lan.

00:10:57.960 --> 00:10:59.120
When I heard Mr. Liu took

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:00.080
this session's exam,

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:01.000
I sent someone

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:02.200
to watch near the exam hall.

00:11:02.270 --> 00:11:03.870
How one acts when the results are posted

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:05.720
shows a person's true color most clearly.

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:08.360
He's at the Fuchun Teahouse.

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:09.870
What a coincidence.

00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:12.000
As you want to inquire about him,

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:13.270
Madame also ordered

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:14.790
me to look into the Liu family,

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:17.030
saying his character comes first.

00:11:17.630 --> 00:11:18.360
My mother

00:11:18.790 --> 00:11:19.720
also asked you?

00:11:20.080 --> 00:11:21.720
Yes. It's only proper

00:11:21.790 --> 00:11:22.840
for her to care about

00:11:22.960 --> 00:11:23.960
your marriage.

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:25.870
I was

00:11:25.870 --> 00:11:26.840
wondering

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.720
whether to report to Mrs. Ji,

00:11:29.150 --> 00:11:29.790
but the servant

00:11:29.790 --> 00:11:31.320
back from Tongzhou said

00:11:31.550 --> 00:11:33.480
she had been ill,

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:35.910
so I hesitated.

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:37.870
Grandmother had been ill?

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:43.720
[The head of the family, Mrs. Ji,]

00:11:43.910 --> 00:11:45.630
[has had several fires set on her property.]

00:11:46.120 --> 00:11:46.840
[Now,]

00:11:47.030 --> 00:11:48.150
[before every meal,]

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:50.080
[she must use a silver needle to test for poison.]

00:11:51.870 --> 00:11:53.200
Don't tell her just yet.

00:11:53.870 --> 00:11:54.390
Yes, Miss.

00:11:55.870 --> 00:11:56.670
Let's go inside.

00:11:57.960 --> 00:11:58.440
Okay.

00:12:02.030 --> 00:12:02.600
Miss,

00:12:03.240 --> 00:12:04.870
that's Liu Xiancheng.

00:12:22.240 --> 00:12:23.910
Isn't that Chen Xuanqing?

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:27.000
I was wondering why there are so many girls.

00:12:27.910 --> 00:12:29.360
Turns out they are here to see him.

00:12:29.480 --> 00:12:30.000
Look,

00:12:30.270 --> 00:12:31.200
that one looks good

00:12:31.870 --> 00:12:33.200
with a pair of dimples.

00:12:34.360 --> 00:12:35.510
The one next to her? No.

00:12:36.670 --> 00:12:37.840
Doesn't deserve to sit here.

00:12:39.030 --> 00:12:39.960
Please be cautious, Mr. Liu.

00:12:43.600 --> 00:12:44.870
What's there to be cautious about?

00:12:45.630 --> 00:12:46.840
These girls chase you

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:48.000
all the way to the exam hall.

00:12:48.870 --> 00:12:49.840
They aren't cautious,

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:50.960
so why should I be?

00:12:51.150 --> 00:12:51.720
Mr. Liu,

00:12:52.120 --> 00:12:52.960
you've got it wrong.

00:12:53.600 --> 00:12:55.080
First, these girls may not

00:12:55.270 --> 00:12:56.240
even be here for me.

00:12:56.630 --> 00:12:57.320
Even if they are,

00:12:57.630 --> 00:12:58.720
they're courteous

00:12:58.960 --> 00:12:59.840
and haven't bothered us.

00:13:01.030 --> 00:13:02.440
For us to scrutinize them

00:13:02.790 --> 00:13:04.000
would violate a gentleman's way.

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:05.480
Moreover,

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:06.960
women already have

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:08.240
a harder time in this world.

00:13:08.630 --> 00:13:09.960
Men shoot their mouths off

00:13:10.240 --> 00:13:11.150
and move on, but if

00:13:12.240 --> 00:13:13.790
those words get out, it could

00:13:14.270 --> 00:13:15.030
become a stain

00:13:15.240 --> 00:13:16.600
on a woman's name

00:13:18.440 --> 00:13:20.200
and no chance for her to defend herself.

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:22.150
We all have sisters.

00:13:22.840 --> 00:13:24.120
Put yourself in their place.

00:13:24.510 --> 00:13:25.720
Be more cautious.

00:13:25.790 --> 00:13:26.440
Fine, fine.

00:13:26.630 --> 00:13:27.510
I won't talk.

00:13:27.910 --> 00:13:29.200
Mr. Liu, I envy your carefree attitude.

00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:31.080
The rest of us are on edge,

00:13:31.360 --> 00:13:32.200
yet you still have

00:13:32.480 --> 00:13:33.840
romance on your mind.

00:13:34.870 --> 00:13:36.600
I wasn't going to pass anyway.

00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:38.670
If my mother hadn't forced me,

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:40.200
I wouldn't have come.

00:13:41.550 --> 00:13:42.600
No wonder Xuanqing

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:43.630
is so well-liked.

00:13:43.750 --> 00:13:45.200
He speaks so convincingly.

00:13:45.480 --> 00:13:46.270
Liu Xiancheng,

00:13:46.270 --> 00:13:47.870
on the other hand, is just too crude.

00:13:48.120 --> 00:13:49.390
Crude? That's putting it mildly.

00:13:50.030 --> 00:13:50.960
On results day,

00:13:51.270 --> 00:13:52.390
a candidate dares to

00:13:52.870 --> 00:13:53.750
act so recklessly

00:13:53.840 --> 00:13:55.000
right in front of the exam hall.

00:13:55.750 --> 00:13:57.120
Either he's got some backing,

00:13:57.750 --> 00:13:59.320
or he's a complete fool.

00:14:13.840 --> 00:14:15.240
The results are out!

00:14:15.240 --> 00:14:15.870
The results are out!

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:16.790
Let's go!

00:14:18.030 --> 00:14:18.510
Xuruo,

00:14:18.510 --> 00:14:19.550
let's go down and take a look.

00:14:19.790 --> 00:14:20.390
Let's go.

00:14:20.480 --> 00:14:21.120
Go, go.

00:14:21.510 --> 00:14:22.030
Look!

00:14:22.150 --> 00:14:22.840
The results are out!

00:14:35.390 --> 00:14:36.000
The results are out!

00:14:36.440 --> 00:14:37.630
Look!

00:14:39.000 --> 00:14:39.630
The results are out!

00:14:39.670 --> 00:14:40.360
Take a good look!

00:14:40.670 --> 00:14:41.320
That's fast!

00:14:41.320 --> 00:14:41.910
Am I included?

00:14:43.550 --> 00:14:44.030
Look!

00:14:47.510 --> 00:14:48.030
Look!

00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:49.320
Am I included?

00:14:49.630 --> 00:14:50.240
Yes!

00:14:53.670 --> 00:14:54.390
Jinzhao, look!

00:14:54.600 --> 00:14:55.240
The results are out!

00:14:58.910 --> 00:14:59.390
Yes!

00:14:59.390 --> 00:14:59.870
Sir,

00:15:00.150 --> 00:15:01.120
why are you still here?

00:15:01.270 --> 00:15:02.390
Let's go down and take a look!

00:15:02.670 --> 00:15:04.790
When the Bingzi provincial exam results

00:15:05.270 --> 00:15:06.080
were announced,

00:15:06.630 --> 00:15:07.840
Uncle Yanyun was waiting right here.

00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:08.750
Today,

00:15:09.750 --> 00:15:10.630
I'll wait here too.

00:15:11.030 --> 00:15:12.150
Then I'll stay with you.

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:25.910
The 49th place of Yiyou

00:15:26.200 --> 00:15:28.390
is Chen Yanwen from Xiheyan Street.

00:15:28.390 --> 00:15:30.030
Wanping County,

00:15:30.510 --> 00:15:31.720
Shuntian Prefecture.

00:15:32.270 --> 00:15:32.840
Elective: The Book of Songs.

00:15:32.840 --> 00:15:33.270
Sir!

00:15:33.270 --> 00:15:33.790
I passed!

00:15:34.120 --> 00:15:34.790
I passed!

00:15:35.390 --> 00:15:36.510
I passed!

00:15:36.910 --> 00:15:38.030
Congratulations!

00:15:38.630 --> 00:15:39.360
It's Mr. Chen Yanwen!

00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:40.790
Sir, your uncle Yanwen passed!

00:15:41.150 --> 00:15:42.510
Shouldn't we congratulate him?

00:15:43.870 --> 00:15:44.360
Xuruo,

00:15:44.960 --> 00:15:45.550
why did your uncle

00:15:45.550 --> 00:15:46.670
also take this exam?

00:15:47.480 --> 00:15:48.030
Congratulations!

00:15:52.000 --> 00:15:52.550
Mr. Liu,

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:54.720
I'll go congratulate my uncle.

00:16:08.510 --> 00:16:09.080
Miss Gu.

00:16:27.870 --> 00:16:28.670
Congratulations!

00:16:28.670 --> 00:16:29.870
Congratulations on passing it!

00:16:31.440 --> 00:16:32.320
Thank you! Thank you!

00:16:32.480 --> 00:16:33.440
Congratulations!

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:34.320
Thank you!

00:16:34.630 --> 00:16:35.960
Thank you, everyone!

00:16:37.030 --> 00:16:37.960
Mr. Jiang found out

00:16:37.960 --> 00:16:39.510
the truth about my father's death,

00:16:40.750 --> 00:16:42.200
so I brought it to you.

00:16:44.790 --> 00:16:45.480
It was

00:16:47.240 --> 00:16:48.480
Uncle Yanwen.

00:16:53.150 --> 00:16:53.790
That day,

00:16:54.720 --> 00:16:55.750
he and my father

00:16:55.750 --> 00:16:56.750
met on a bridge.

00:16:57.030 --> 00:16:57.910
They argued.

00:16:58.670 --> 00:16:59.750
Uncle Yanwen pushed

00:16:59.750 --> 00:17:00.870
my father into a pond.

00:17:01.720 --> 00:17:03.270
He struggled to the bank

00:17:03.790 --> 00:17:05.069
and nearly got out of the water,

00:17:06.829 --> 00:17:08.030
but Uncle Yanwen

00:17:08.550 --> 00:17:10.000
pried his fingers open

00:17:11.200 --> 00:17:12.550
and pushed him off again.

00:17:14.550 --> 00:17:15.480
Congratulations!

00:17:15.720 --> 00:17:16.640
Congrats!

00:17:18.790 --> 00:17:19.750
Congratulations!

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:20.880
Sir,

00:17:21.270 --> 00:17:22.640
shouldn't we go congratulate?

00:17:23.200 --> 00:17:23.750
Never mind,

00:17:24.790 --> 00:17:25.510
let's just stay here.

00:17:26.000 --> 00:17:26.960
Thank you!

00:17:28.790 --> 00:17:30.200
I'll treat you later!

00:17:30.310 --> 00:17:31.160
Congrats!

00:17:31.160 --> 00:17:32.030
Congratulations!

00:17:32.070 --> 00:17:32.920
Congrats!

00:17:32.920 --> 00:17:33.790
Congratulations!

00:17:33.920 --> 00:17:35.310
Congratulations!

00:17:35.440 --> 00:17:36.240
Congratulations!

00:17:39.070 --> 00:17:40.160
The 3rd place of Yiyou

00:17:40.550 --> 00:17:41.790
is Zhuang Zhengyu

00:17:42.310 --> 00:17:44.510
from Xisipailou,

00:17:44.920 --> 00:17:46.270
Wanping County,

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:48.160
Shuntian Prefecture.

00:17:48.720 --> 00:17:49.880
- Elective: The Book of Documents.
- It's me!

00:17:49.960 --> 00:17:50.480
It's me!

00:17:50.550 --> 00:17:52.240
I passed!

00:17:52.270 --> 00:17:53.350
Congratulations!

00:17:54.550 --> 00:17:55.880
Thank you! Thank you!

00:17:56.000 --> 00:17:57.350
Only the top two are left.

00:17:58.000 --> 00:17:59.830
Liu Xiancheng definitely won't make it.

00:18:00.240 --> 00:18:00.680
But there's

00:18:00.880 --> 00:18:02.550
still no Chen Xuanqing.

00:18:02.720 --> 00:18:04.720
He couldn't have failed, could he?

00:18:05.790 --> 00:18:06.830
The 2nd place of Yiyou

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:08.160
is Liu Kezuan

00:18:08.590 --> 00:18:12.240
from Xiaowang Town, Gaoyang County,

00:18:12.440 --> 00:18:13.550
Baoping Prefecture.

00:18:14.110 --> 00:18:15.000
Elective: The Book of Rites.

00:18:15.750 --> 00:18:16.960
It's me!

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:18.000
Congratulations!

00:18:18.110 --> 00:18:19.200
Thank you!

00:18:19.510 --> 00:18:20.030
Thank you!

00:18:20.880 --> 00:18:21.720
Congratulations!

00:18:21.720 --> 00:18:22.310
Congrats!

00:18:22.310 --> 00:18:23.400
The 1st place of Yiyou,

00:18:23.590 --> 00:18:24.590
with elective:

00:18:24.920 --> 00:18:26.030
The Spring and Autumn Annals,

00:18:30.830 --> 00:18:33.240
is the one from Xiheyan Street,

00:18:33.550 --> 00:18:35.110
Wanping County,

00:18:38.480 --> 00:18:40.030
Shuntian Prefecture—

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.270
Chen Xuanqing.

00:18:43.880 --> 00:18:44.750
Sir! Sir!

00:18:44.750 --> 00:18:45.480
It's you!

00:18:45.680 --> 00:18:47.830
You're in the first place!

00:18:50.830 --> 00:18:51.960
Here's the winner!

00:18:52.110 --> 00:18:53.240
Here's the winner!

00:18:53.480 --> 00:18:54.350
Here he is!

00:18:57.000 --> 00:18:57.830
Congratulations!

00:18:58.590 --> 00:19:00.160
Congratulations to the winner!

00:19:00.510 --> 00:19:01.270
Congratulations!

00:19:01.270 --> 00:19:02.350
Congratulations!

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:03.750
Congratulations!

00:19:03.830 --> 00:19:05.070
Congratulations!

00:19:05.070 --> 00:19:05.720
Congratulats!

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:06.720
Congratulations!

00:19:32.480 --> 00:19:32.880
Sir,

00:19:33.270 --> 00:19:33.960
here's

00:19:33.960 --> 00:19:34.960
the autumn exam pass list.

00:19:35.070 --> 00:19:35.590
Please take a look.

00:19:44.200 --> 00:19:46.440
He's being too conspicuous.

00:19:47.960 --> 00:19:49.000
Passing is enough.

00:19:49.310 --> 00:19:51.030
Why did he aim for the first place?

00:19:52.400 --> 00:19:53.200
As for Yanwen,

00:19:54.240 --> 00:19:55.440
he doesn't live up to this.

00:19:59.480 --> 00:20:00.680
There's nothing we can do about it.

00:20:01.030 --> 00:20:02.160
The Shuntian chief examiner

00:20:02.350 --> 00:20:03.830
has long wanted your favor.

00:20:04.200 --> 00:20:04.830
This time, it just

00:20:04.960 --> 00:20:05.640
happens to coincide

00:20:05.640 --> 00:20:07.270
that Xuanqing and Yanwen are taking the exam.

00:20:07.750 --> 00:20:09.400
Of course he's eager to curry favor.

00:20:10.480 --> 00:20:11.790
I've read Yanwen's essay.

00:20:12.270 --> 00:20:13.200
Passing or not,

00:20:13.350 --> 00:20:14.830
it could go either way.

00:20:15.480 --> 00:20:16.550
Thanks to you,

00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:17.830
of course he passed.

00:20:17.960 --> 00:20:19.000
That's what I'm worried about.

00:20:19.270 --> 00:20:20.000
Next spring

00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:21.240
he'll surely take the exams.

00:20:21.590 --> 00:20:22.510
What if he meets

00:20:22.510 --> 00:20:23.790
an ambitious

00:20:24.070 --> 00:20:25.160
chief examiner?

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:27.510
Are you worried about him

00:20:27.790 --> 00:20:28.750
because of the Fifth Master?

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:30.720
You know Yanwen.

00:20:31.240 --> 00:20:32.510
He'll get himself trouble

00:20:33.310 --> 00:20:34.240
once he enters officialdom.

00:20:43.590 --> 00:20:44.200
What happened?

00:20:44.920 --> 00:20:46.400
Sir, the axle is broken.

00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:47.830
Can it be repaired?

00:20:48.200 --> 00:20:48.640
Yes.

00:20:49.030 --> 00:20:49.830
It'll only take a quarter.

00:20:52.880 --> 00:20:53.920
Send someone to check

00:20:54.030 --> 00:20:55.350
if Lan has finished picking.

00:20:55.680 --> 00:20:56.680
If so,

00:20:56.680 --> 00:20:58.110
tell her we should go back.

00:20:59.550 --> 00:21:00.550
Besides the crate of Wu silk

00:21:00.750 --> 00:21:02.310
and the crate of plain gauze

00:21:02.440 --> 00:21:03.480
I just picked,

00:21:03.880 --> 00:21:05.000
go to Simingzhai

00:21:05.160 --> 00:21:06.350
and choose two Song carvings.

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:07.680
And our Linxia House's

00:21:07.680 --> 00:21:08.590
new pastries.

00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:10.640
Pack them in an eight-treasure box,

00:21:10.830 --> 00:21:12.070
and send it to the Chen residence.

00:21:12.200 --> 00:21:12.830
Understood?

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:17.240
When giving gifts,

00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:18.510
we must send the very best.

00:21:18.510 --> 00:21:19.000
Yes, Miss.

00:21:24.240 --> 00:21:25.200
[It's Chen Yanyun.]

00:21:27.480 --> 00:21:28.350
Can you handle it?

00:21:29.480 --> 00:21:30.350
Don't worry, sir.

00:21:48.400 --> 00:21:49.550
Congratulations, sir.

00:21:49.680 --> 00:21:51.200
I heard Chen Xuanqing

00:21:51.270 --> 00:21:52.110
and Chen Yanwen

00:21:52.350 --> 00:21:53.550
both passed the imperial exams.

00:21:54.270 --> 00:21:55.160
Congratulations.

00:21:55.640 --> 00:21:56.880
I've prepared gifts

00:21:57.350 --> 00:21:58.070
and had someone

00:21:58.270 --> 00:21:59.640
all sent to the Chen residence.

00:22:01.070 --> 00:22:02.440
Thank you for your trouble.

00:22:23.680 --> 00:22:24.680
Would you like a piece?

00:22:24.960 --> 00:22:25.880
This jujube pastry

00:22:26.000 --> 00:22:26.480
is made by

00:22:26.480 --> 00:22:27.750
our shop's chef.

00:22:28.440 --> 00:22:29.480
You can't buy it elsewhere.

00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:35.480
Sir,

00:22:35.960 --> 00:22:36.920
it's done.

00:22:38.790 --> 00:22:40.200
[It's because of his broken carriage.]

00:22:53.000 --> 00:22:53.720
That's enough.

00:22:54.680 --> 00:22:55.270
Thank you.

00:23:02.400 --> 00:23:03.920
[He is so strange]

00:23:04.240 --> 00:23:05.680
[and hard to read.]

00:23:08.960 --> 00:23:09.510
Miss,

00:23:10.160 --> 00:23:11.110
Mr. Chen

00:23:11.750 --> 00:23:12.920
seems a bit

00:23:13.070 --> 00:23:14.270
unhappy.

00:23:14.310 --> 00:23:15.270
You also think so?

00:23:17.440 --> 00:23:18.510
Looks like the Chen family

00:23:18.640 --> 00:23:19.750
has plenty of secrets.

00:23:21.310 --> 00:23:21.790
Look,

00:23:22.070 --> 00:23:23.160
don't send those four

00:23:23.270 --> 00:23:23.960
I picked.

00:23:24.640 --> 00:23:26.590
Just pick four

00:23:26.720 --> 00:23:27.640
ordinary ones.

00:23:28.030 --> 00:23:28.790
No rush.

00:23:29.000 --> 00:23:30.550
Send them quietly

00:23:30.720 --> 00:23:32.510
with the rest of their guests.

00:23:32.720 --> 00:23:33.240
Yes, Miss.

00:23:38.070 --> 00:23:38.960
Why are you

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:40.350
so happy today?

00:23:41.200 --> 00:23:41.680
The autumn

00:23:42.070 --> 00:23:43.030
exam results came out.

00:23:44.070 --> 00:23:45.680
Liu Xiancheng didn't pass.

00:23:46.030 --> 00:23:46.750
That makes

00:23:47.790 --> 00:23:49.070
this marriage

00:23:49.400 --> 00:23:49.920
secure.

00:23:50.680 --> 00:23:51.790
No wonder they sent his birth-date

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:53.000
betrothal slip

00:23:53.000 --> 00:23:53.720
right over

00:23:53.720 --> 00:23:54.640
in the afternoon.

00:23:54.830 --> 00:23:56.030
It's because he failed the exam.

00:23:58.350 --> 00:24:00.240
People are always like that.

00:24:00.510 --> 00:24:01.790
Nothing surprising.

00:24:02.110 --> 00:24:02.750
It won't be too late

00:24:03.160 --> 00:24:04.110
to marry Jinzhao to him

00:24:04.110 --> 00:24:05.270
after he passes the exams later.

00:24:05.640 --> 00:24:06.480
He won't pass.

00:24:06.680 --> 00:24:07.880
I had people inquire.

00:24:08.550 --> 00:24:09.830
This boy

00:24:10.400 --> 00:24:11.720
is lecherous.

00:24:12.680 --> 00:24:13.880
Young as he is,

00:24:14.110 --> 00:24:15.830
he already keeps several chamber maids

00:24:16.440 --> 00:24:17.510
and even a mistress outside

00:24:17.510 --> 00:24:18.480
for nearly a year.

00:24:19.480 --> 00:24:20.550
How can such a person

00:24:20.790 --> 00:24:22.030
pass the exams?

00:24:23.790 --> 00:24:24.640
Is this match

00:24:25.160 --> 00:24:26.070
still worth pursuing?

00:24:26.270 --> 00:24:27.510
A man being lustful

00:24:28.160 --> 00:24:28.880
is nothing

00:24:29.480 --> 00:24:30.960
but a minor flaw.

00:24:31.590 --> 00:24:33.590
This boy may be disappointing,

00:24:34.240 --> 00:24:35.750
but his father is not.

00:24:36.880 --> 00:24:38.200
Word's already out.

00:24:38.510 --> 00:24:40.030
The Junior Vice Minister of Revenue

00:24:40.750 --> 00:24:41.790
is bound to be his father,

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:43.790
Liu Siyu.

00:24:44.160 --> 00:24:45.070
Really?

00:24:45.510 --> 00:24:47.440
With this marriage connection,

00:24:47.960 --> 00:24:49.550
even if I don't get praised

00:24:50.590 --> 00:24:52.680
in this performance review,

00:24:53.110 --> 00:24:53.550
at least

00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:57.440
a passable rating is safe.

00:25:00.550 --> 00:25:01.030
Come on.

00:25:07.070 --> 00:25:08.550
Why are you sighing?

00:25:08.830 --> 00:25:10.400
What does Mrs. Ji's reply say?

00:25:12.030 --> 00:25:13.920
She didn't say it outright.

00:25:14.960 --> 00:25:16.480
It's an unsaid understanding.

00:25:19.240 --> 00:25:20.400
For now, we should focus on

00:25:20.590 --> 00:25:21.830
this marriage arrangement.

00:25:23.790 --> 00:25:24.480
The Liu sent over

00:25:24.480 --> 00:25:25.750
the birth-date betrothal

00:25:25.750 --> 00:25:26.750
slip today.

00:25:27.350 --> 00:25:28.920
Mistress Song even asked Madame

00:25:28.920 --> 00:25:30.720
for your birth details.

00:25:31.270 --> 00:25:32.510
But Madame hasn't given her yet,

00:25:32.920 --> 00:25:34.830
saying she needed to think it over.

00:25:35.480 --> 00:25:36.720
Once the slips are exchanged,

00:25:36.880 --> 00:25:37.790
backing out

00:25:38.070 --> 00:25:39.160
would cause

00:25:39.270 --> 00:25:40.310
bad rumors.

00:25:41.030 --> 00:25:42.590
Anyway, no matter what they do,

00:25:43.030 --> 00:25:43.880
I won't ever marry

00:25:43.880 --> 00:25:44.830
into the Liu family.

00:25:45.350 --> 00:25:46.200
Madame is too soft

00:25:46.400 --> 00:25:47.350
and has no real power.

00:25:47.830 --> 00:25:48.960
Speaking to her is useless.

00:25:51.510 --> 00:25:52.880
Grandmother is ill,

00:25:53.160 --> 00:25:54.070
yet she didn't mention it

00:25:54.270 --> 00:25:55.240
at all in her letter.

00:25:56.790 --> 00:25:58.000
The more she's like this,

00:25:59.160 --> 00:26:00.830
the less I should trouble her.

00:26:02.640 --> 00:26:04.030
If it really comes down to it,

00:26:05.000 --> 00:26:06.310
I'll fight our way out

00:26:06.720 --> 00:26:07.720
and back to Tongzhou.

00:26:07.960 --> 00:26:08.880
Who cares about the Liu!

00:26:11.110 --> 00:26:12.070
Keep that move

00:26:12.070 --> 00:26:13.400
for the very end of our rope.

00:26:17.110 --> 00:26:18.110
For now,

00:26:19.160 --> 00:26:20.750
there are two men who can help.

00:26:21.920 --> 00:26:22.720
Who are they?

00:26:40.270 --> 00:26:41.440
This Rain of Pear Blossom

00:26:41.510 --> 00:26:42.310
Needles devised by

00:26:42.310 --> 00:26:43.480
Mr. Xiao is deadly.

00:26:43.680 --> 00:26:45.350
If I hadn't been wearing chest armor,

00:26:45.350 --> 00:26:46.440
I would be dead for sure.

00:26:47.510 --> 00:26:48.750
So I should coat these needles

00:26:48.750 --> 00:26:49.790
with a potent poison.

00:26:50.510 --> 00:26:52.310
Then I wouldn't need to aim for the chest,

00:26:53.830 --> 00:26:55.680
but a scratch

00:26:55.880 --> 00:26:57.160
would be fatal.

00:26:58.240 --> 00:26:59.310
We'll test it later.

00:26:59.920 --> 00:27:01.550
Who to test it on?

00:27:03.310 --> 00:27:03.720
Hey!

00:27:04.030 --> 00:27:05.480
Sir, don't look at me!

00:27:05.550 --> 00:27:06.200
I...

00:27:09.640 --> 00:27:11.160
There is actually someone.

00:27:11.720 --> 00:27:12.480
Shut up!

00:27:13.000 --> 00:27:13.750
Say that again,

00:27:14.110 --> 00:27:15.200
and I might not be able to stop myself

00:27:15.400 --> 00:27:16.030
from seeking justice

00:27:16.200 --> 00:27:17.030
for this horse.

00:27:20.720 --> 00:27:22.310
Sir. Master has returned.

00:27:22.310 --> 00:27:23.000
He's waiting for you.

00:27:30.110 --> 00:27:31.400
Why did you give away

00:27:31.400 --> 00:27:32.310
your personal sword?

00:27:32.550 --> 00:27:33.110
That

00:27:33.110 --> 00:27:34.440
should have been kept for Xian.

00:27:35.680 --> 00:27:36.680
Kept for him?

00:27:37.720 --> 00:27:39.110
Could he even lift it?

00:27:39.750 --> 00:27:41.070
Look at that scrawny frame.

00:27:41.510 --> 00:27:42.920
He'll never wield a sword in this lifetime.

00:27:43.070 --> 00:27:43.960
I know.

00:27:44.270 --> 00:27:45.350
You blame me for not

00:27:45.960 --> 00:27:47.750
giving you a son to be a general on horseback.

00:27:51.830 --> 00:27:52.510
Dear,

00:27:53.640 --> 00:27:54.510
don't be angry.

00:27:55.070 --> 00:27:55.510
Come on.

00:27:56.480 --> 00:27:57.000
Sir.

00:28:02.070 --> 00:28:02.880
Let him know I'm here.

00:28:03.110 --> 00:28:03.590
Yes, sir.

00:28:06.240 --> 00:28:07.270
Master. Ma'am.

00:28:07.480 --> 00:28:08.310
Here comes the young master.

00:28:15.350 --> 00:28:16.510
Master. Ma'am.

00:28:16.720 --> 00:28:18.590
Father. Mother.

00:28:21.790 --> 00:28:23.480
I heard you're tinkering with hidden weapons again.

00:28:24.110 --> 00:28:25.590
Tricks and gadgets.

00:28:26.070 --> 00:28:27.160
Even if you can't ride a horse,

00:28:27.160 --> 00:28:27.920
or wield a sword,

00:28:27.960 --> 00:28:29.270
you should still learn military texts.

00:28:29.680 --> 00:28:30.480
What do we

00:28:30.480 --> 00:28:31.720
martial nobles rely on?

00:28:31.960 --> 00:28:33.720
Real military merit!

00:28:34.790 --> 00:28:35.510
Enough.

00:28:35.790 --> 00:28:36.790
First thing first.

00:28:38.480 --> 00:28:39.590
His Majesty has appointed you

00:28:40.590 --> 00:28:41.720
as the Crown Prince's companion.

00:28:42.720 --> 00:28:44.030
Go pack. Tomorrow, you

00:28:44.030 --> 00:28:45.030
come with me to the palace.

00:28:45.590 --> 00:28:46.720
The Crown Prince's companion?

00:28:47.480 --> 00:28:48.160
Why would His Majesty

00:28:48.160 --> 00:28:49.270
think of me out of the blue?

00:28:50.480 --> 00:28:51.880
Why you?

00:28:52.550 --> 00:28:54.480
Because the Office thought you're

00:28:54.550 --> 00:28:55.440
at the perfect age.

00:28:55.440 --> 00:28:56.310
So you're going.

00:28:58.750 --> 00:28:59.830
It's Chen Yanyun.

00:29:00.920 --> 00:29:01.880
Listen well.

00:29:02.310 --> 00:29:03.400
To accompany the Crown Prince,

00:29:03.960 --> 00:29:05.000
you must be careful with

00:29:05.110 --> 00:29:06.000
your behavior and learn hard.

00:29:07.790 --> 00:29:09.070
Learn what?

00:29:09.200 --> 00:29:10.790
Learn whatever you're told to learn!

00:29:11.590 --> 00:29:12.510
What about military texts?

00:29:12.680 --> 00:29:13.110
You!

00:29:14.510 --> 00:29:15.880
- Sir!
- You're asking for trouble!

00:29:20.830 --> 00:29:22.270
What are you doing?

00:29:30.240 --> 00:29:31.000
Tomorrow morning,

00:29:31.750 --> 00:29:33.350
send someone to deliver this letter

00:29:33.350 --> 00:29:34.310
to the Changxing.

00:29:34.550 --> 00:29:35.510
How can that be?

00:29:35.680 --> 00:29:36.550
It's so important.

00:29:36.640 --> 00:29:37.920
I'd better deliver it myself.

00:29:38.160 --> 00:29:38.680
No need.

00:29:38.790 --> 00:29:40.000
Just send anyone.

00:29:40.680 --> 00:29:42.110
If the letter doesn't arrive,

00:29:42.640 --> 00:29:43.880
send this one

00:29:44.270 --> 00:29:45.310
to Ye Xian.

00:29:47.960 --> 00:29:49.590
Are you trying to...

00:29:50.070 --> 00:29:51.750
Haven't we always wanted to find out

00:29:52.000 --> 00:29:53.070
who the lurker is?

00:29:54.400 --> 00:29:55.440
Then,

00:29:55.640 --> 00:29:58.110
let's lure the snake out of its hole.

00:30:14.510 --> 00:30:15.400
Huang?

00:30:18.270 --> 00:30:19.640
You have great taste, young lady.

00:30:26.000 --> 00:30:27.160
Miss Gu

00:30:27.720 --> 00:30:29.440
is grasping at straws.

00:30:30.160 --> 00:30:32.030
How could the Changxing heir

00:30:32.550 --> 00:30:34.160
ever help with that?

00:30:37.030 --> 00:30:38.310
Who knows.

00:30:42.480 --> 00:30:44.110
Dispose of this letter, Chen Yi.

00:30:45.830 --> 00:30:46.880
Not to send it to

00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:48.030
the Changxing as is?

00:30:48.240 --> 00:30:48.920
No.

00:30:50.000 --> 00:30:51.550
The one she really meant to send

00:30:52.110 --> 00:30:53.480
has probably already arrived.

00:30:53.720 --> 00:30:54.680
Sorry,

00:30:55.200 --> 00:30:55.750
but I don't get it.

00:30:56.510 --> 00:30:57.920
Your mole is probably

00:30:58.400 --> 00:30:59.960
already blown.

00:31:01.000 --> 00:31:01.640
No way!

00:31:02.480 --> 00:31:04.110
She's at most gotten

00:31:04.110 --> 00:31:05.000
suspicious.

00:31:05.400 --> 00:31:07.400
No way she knows who it is!

00:31:07.790 --> 00:31:08.440
Then let me ask.

00:31:08.680 --> 00:31:10.270
Last time, Miss Gu's letter

00:31:10.270 --> 00:31:11.750
to Mrs. Ji

00:31:11.880 --> 00:31:13.160
was sealed with wax.

00:31:13.830 --> 00:31:15.160
This time, none.

00:31:15.750 --> 00:31:16.550
What do you think?

00:31:19.160 --> 00:31:20.270
That maid beside Miss Gu

00:31:20.310 --> 00:31:21.070
knows martial arts, right?

00:31:21.200 --> 00:31:21.960
Maybe she's

00:31:22.160 --> 00:31:22.880
already

00:31:22.880 --> 00:31:24.350
tailed your men.

00:31:25.400 --> 00:31:25.880
Sir, forgive me.

00:31:26.400 --> 00:31:28.030
I deserve death for my mistake.

00:31:28.200 --> 00:31:29.270
Not quite,

00:31:29.270 --> 00:31:30.440
but there are indeed lapses.

00:31:30.750 --> 00:31:32.000
Go receive your punishment.

00:31:32.510 --> 00:31:34.510
As for those watching Gu Jinzhao.

00:31:34.720 --> 00:31:35.510
Pull them back.

00:31:35.750 --> 00:31:36.200
Yes, sir.

00:31:44.790 --> 00:31:46.070
This Gu Jinzhao

00:31:47.480 --> 00:31:48.480
is truly clever.

00:31:48.790 --> 00:31:49.480
Clever,

00:31:50.070 --> 00:31:51.000
and bold too.

00:31:51.440 --> 00:31:52.750
She's scheming against me as well.

00:31:54.750 --> 00:31:56.400
You think this letter

00:31:56.400 --> 00:31:57.880
was just for Ye Xian?

00:31:59.070 --> 00:31:59.720
No way!

00:32:01.070 --> 00:32:02.270
She thought you'd

00:32:02.720 --> 00:32:03.830
help her too

00:32:03.830 --> 00:32:04.830
after reading it?

00:32:07.790 --> 00:32:08.790
Would you?

00:32:09.000 --> 00:32:09.880
No.

00:32:10.240 --> 00:32:10.960
Of course not!

00:32:11.590 --> 00:32:13.000
That thought of hers

00:32:13.000 --> 00:32:14.400
is just too arrogant.

00:32:14.830 --> 00:32:16.400
To you, it's arrogance.

00:32:16.750 --> 00:32:18.310
To her, it's an opportunity.

00:32:18.720 --> 00:32:20.440
One letter, but shown to two people.

00:32:20.830 --> 00:32:22.550
If even one of them agrees to help,

00:32:22.830 --> 00:32:23.680
she wins.

00:32:24.640 --> 00:32:25.720
Why not do it?

00:32:26.830 --> 00:32:28.030
Indeed.

00:32:29.880 --> 00:32:31.110
A trades-person's way of thinking

00:32:31.110 --> 00:32:32.030
is completely different

00:32:32.030 --> 00:32:32.790
from a scholar's.

00:32:33.310 --> 00:32:35.110
There are plenty of scholars at court.

00:32:35.480 --> 00:32:37.160
If half knew how to do trade,

00:32:38.030 --> 00:32:39.790
the treasury wouldn't be so empty.

00:32:43.310 --> 00:32:44.750
This Gu Jinzhao

00:32:45.240 --> 00:32:46.720
has something of

00:32:46.720 --> 00:32:48.160
Mrs. Ji's style about her.

00:32:49.030 --> 00:32:50.440
No wonder you wanted

00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:52.750
to test her.

00:32:54.350 --> 00:32:55.750
Suddenly I feel

00:32:56.000 --> 00:32:57.400
it'd be a pity

00:32:57.400 --> 00:32:58.680
to withdraw the mole.

00:32:58.790 --> 00:32:59.720
What do you mean?

00:33:01.880 --> 00:33:03.350
It's been a while

00:33:03.680 --> 00:33:05.350
since I've seen you this happy.

00:33:12.550 --> 00:33:14.240
It's the driver, Huang.

00:33:15.240 --> 00:33:16.270
Huang?

00:33:17.480 --> 00:33:18.510
It's actually him?

00:33:19.400 --> 00:33:20.720
When we were in danger in the capital,

00:33:21.270 --> 00:33:22.550
I saw how quickly he reacted.

00:33:22.880 --> 00:33:24.350
I thought it's just because he's skilled.

00:33:25.070 --> 00:33:26.070
But thinking back,

00:33:26.310 --> 00:33:27.640
he probably knows martial arts.

00:33:28.160 --> 00:33:29.790
I gave the letter to the Changxing.

00:33:30.310 --> 00:33:31.400
Bodyguard Li,

00:33:31.400 --> 00:33:32.590
who serves Ye Xian, told me

00:33:32.720 --> 00:33:33.880
Ye Xian has entered the palace

00:33:34.030 --> 00:33:35.440
as the Crown Prince's companion

00:33:35.790 --> 00:33:36.960
and can't come out

00:33:36.960 --> 00:33:37.790
until his rest day,

00:33:38.200 --> 00:33:39.030
which means we should wait

00:33:40.440 --> 00:33:41.240
at least a month.

00:33:41.510 --> 00:33:42.440
A month?

00:33:44.160 --> 00:33:45.270
That's too long.

00:33:51.480 --> 00:33:52.550
I need another idea.

00:33:53.000 --> 00:33:53.510
Qingpu,

00:33:53.680 --> 00:33:54.590
go keep an eye on the Liu.

00:34:01.720 --> 00:34:03.160
Rest for a quarter.

00:34:09.070 --> 00:34:10.230
Bring Frost over.

00:34:11.030 --> 00:34:12.510
Here comes Frost!

00:34:14.400 --> 00:34:14.920
Frost!

00:34:14.920 --> 00:34:15.630
Go catch it!

00:34:15.760 --> 00:34:16.510
Stop!

00:34:16.760 --> 00:34:17.760
Go catch it!

00:34:18.070 --> 00:34:19.030
Frost is there!

00:34:19.230 --> 00:34:20.190
It's over there!

00:34:21.400 --> 00:34:22.360
Go catch it!

00:34:23.000 --> 00:34:23.880
It's over there!

00:34:28.880 --> 00:34:29.550
Come on!

00:34:30.590 --> 00:34:31.280
There!

00:34:31.280 --> 00:34:31.670
There!

00:34:32.400 --> 00:34:33.280
Over there!

00:34:41.190 --> 00:34:41.800
Quick!

00:34:41.800 --> 00:34:42.440
Surround it!

00:34:46.070 --> 00:34:46.710
Frost!

00:34:46.880 --> 00:34:47.360
Come here!

00:35:00.840 --> 00:35:02.030
Mr. Ye is so capable.

00:35:02.480 --> 00:35:03.320
In just a few days,

00:35:03.880 --> 00:35:04.590
you have Frost

00:35:04.760 --> 00:35:06.030
completely tamed.

00:35:06.900 --> 00:35:08.960
I merely used a trivial trick.

00:35:11.670 --> 00:35:13.440
It's honey!

00:35:14.150 --> 00:35:16.000
Thank you for the lesson, Mr. Ye.

00:35:18.070 --> 00:35:18.670
Your Highness.

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:19.710
Mr. Ye.

00:35:20.070 --> 00:35:21.190
You have a letter.

00:35:25.920 --> 00:35:27.440
[I wanted to refuse outright,]

00:35:28.110 --> 00:35:30.150
[but I hear the Liu family is related to the marquisate.]

00:35:30.710 --> 00:35:31.880
[Making a scene would be a small matter,]

00:35:32.510 --> 00:35:34.000
[while hurting the marquisate's face is not.]

00:35:38.000 --> 00:35:39.070
Threatening me?

00:35:40.590 --> 00:35:41.960
What nerve!

00:35:42.480 --> 00:35:43.230
Sir, I'll take my leave

00:35:43.440 --> 00:35:44.510
if there's nothing else.

00:36:10.960 --> 00:36:12.400
Amazing!

00:36:13.030 --> 00:36:15.280
That's just so amazing!

00:36:15.920 --> 00:36:17.480
His Highness bestows a reward!

00:36:18.480 --> 00:36:19.710
It's mine! It's mine!

00:36:19.960 --> 00:36:21.070
Quick!

00:36:22.440 --> 00:36:23.360
Ye Xian,

00:36:23.360 --> 00:36:24.320
look at these scoundrels.

00:36:24.760 --> 00:36:26.800
Quick! Whoever grabs it keeps it.

00:36:27.440 --> 00:36:28.710
Mine, mine!

00:36:29.320 --> 00:36:29.920
What?

00:36:30.190 --> 00:36:31.480
Mr. Chen is here?

00:36:31.480 --> 00:36:32.030
Mine!

00:36:32.320 --> 00:36:32.920
Quick!

00:36:32.920 --> 00:36:33.550
Put these away!

00:36:33.880 --> 00:36:34.480
Move!

00:36:34.960 --> 00:36:35.840
Come here, this way!

00:36:35.840 --> 00:36:36.670
Quick, quick!

00:36:36.670 --> 00:36:37.590
Quick, quick!

00:36:37.920 --> 00:36:38.840
Put these away!

00:36:39.510 --> 00:36:40.880
Over there!

00:36:57.150 --> 00:36:58.670
Chen Yanyun, Chief of the Crown Prince's Office

00:36:58.670 --> 00:37:00.670
and Lecturer to the Eastern Palace,

00:37:00.670 --> 00:37:03.000
requests an audience with His Highness.

00:37:21.480 --> 00:37:22.070
Your servant

00:37:22.960 --> 00:37:24.590
kowtows to Your Highness.

00:37:25.550 --> 00:37:26.550
Rise, Mr. Chen.

00:37:28.320 --> 00:37:29.190
I was just reading

00:37:29.440 --> 00:37:31.480
Direct Explanations of the Four Books

00:37:32.230 --> 00:37:33.550
and recalled that you once said: extending

00:37:34.030 --> 00:37:35.190
knowledge comes from the Great Learning,

00:37:35.840 --> 00:37:37.710
and innate knowledge comes from Mencius.

00:37:38.230 --> 00:37:39.030
I've gained some insight.

00:38:02.630 --> 00:38:03.880
Your Highness.

00:38:04.590 --> 00:38:05.880
You neglected your studies

00:38:06.150 --> 00:38:07.400
and falsified things.

00:38:07.920 --> 00:38:08.710
According to the rules,

00:38:09.280 --> 00:38:09.880
you should be

00:38:10.360 --> 00:38:11.630
punished with three strikes on the palm.

00:38:12.440 --> 00:38:13.070
Does Your Highness

00:38:13.760 --> 00:38:14.550
have any objection?

00:38:15.880 --> 00:38:17.670
N-no.

00:38:18.510 --> 00:38:19.030
Good.

00:38:19.840 --> 00:38:20.360
Take the tool.

00:38:20.400 --> 00:38:20.960
Wait.

00:38:21.960 --> 00:38:22.550
What?

00:38:23.070 --> 00:38:24.230
What do you want to say?

00:38:25.400 --> 00:38:26.920
You saw His Highness playing

00:38:27.150 --> 00:38:28.800
and assumed he has neglected his studies.

00:38:29.400 --> 00:38:30.320
What you don't know is that

00:38:30.320 --> 00:38:31.280
His Highness rose at three,

00:38:31.710 --> 00:38:32.480
first studied two hours

00:38:32.480 --> 00:38:33.440
with Lecturer Wang,

00:38:33.800 --> 00:38:34.760
then continued reading

00:38:34.760 --> 00:38:35.880
until afternoon.

00:38:36.710 --> 00:38:37.880
Still underage, His Highness

00:38:38.110 --> 00:38:39.760
sleeps barely three hours a night.

00:38:40.230 --> 00:38:41.230
His workload is far heavier

00:38:41.590 --> 00:38:42.880
than that of ordinary scholars.

00:38:43.590 --> 00:38:45.280
He just relaxes briefly.

00:38:45.760 --> 00:38:46.510
Mr. Chen,

00:38:47.360 --> 00:38:48.800
why be so harsh?

00:38:49.280 --> 00:38:49.920
His Highness

00:38:50.400 --> 00:38:51.230
is the Crown Prince,

00:38:51.760 --> 00:38:53.110
not ordinary scholar.

00:38:53.440 --> 00:38:54.360
That's the first point.

00:38:56.360 --> 00:38:57.840
If His Highness finds

00:38:58.190 --> 00:38:59.880
the workload too heavy,

00:39:00.190 --> 00:39:02.000
he could simply order me to revise the schedule.

00:39:03.320 --> 00:39:04.400
Instead, he hid the truth

00:39:04.630 --> 00:39:06.000
from me with his servants' help.

00:39:07.280 --> 00:39:08.280
My punishment

00:39:08.800 --> 00:39:10.400
is not for playing.

00:39:11.000 --> 00:39:12.960
It's for deceiving himself and others.

00:39:13.320 --> 00:39:14.230
That's the second point.

00:39:14.920 --> 00:39:15.590
Does Your Highness

00:39:16.320 --> 00:39:17.480
accept the punishment?

00:39:18.590 --> 00:39:19.800
You're right, sir.

00:39:20.710 --> 00:39:21.710
I accept the punishment.

00:39:22.030 --> 00:39:23.070
Alright. Take the tool.

00:39:23.400 --> 00:39:23.960
Wait.

00:39:25.230 --> 00:39:26.590
As His Highness's companion,

00:39:26.920 --> 00:39:28.000
I can't bear to see him punished.

00:39:28.590 --> 00:39:29.670
I'll take the punishment in his place.

00:39:30.280 --> 00:39:30.920
Ye Xian.

00:39:34.800 --> 00:39:35.670
Mr. Ye

00:39:36.760 --> 00:39:37.800
is truly loyal.

00:39:41.800 --> 00:39:42.550
But unfortunately,

00:39:43.070 --> 00:39:44.360
you're not qualified to take

00:39:45.000 --> 00:39:46.190
His Highness's punishment.

00:39:47.550 --> 00:39:48.630
As his companion,

00:39:48.630 --> 00:39:49.880
your failure to counsel him

00:39:51.190 --> 00:39:52.360
already warrants punishment.

00:39:56.920 --> 00:39:57.630
The tool!

00:39:58.000 --> 00:39:59.190
Crown Prince,

00:39:59.590 --> 00:40:00.510
three strikes on the hand.

00:40:01.840 --> 00:40:02.590
Mr. Ye,

00:40:03.230 --> 00:40:04.280
thirty.

00:40:07.510 --> 00:40:08.920
Mr. Ye, forgive me.

00:40:14.670 --> 00:40:15.630
Twelve.

00:40:28.360 --> 00:40:31.230
Twenty-seven, twenty-eight, twenty-nine.

00:40:31.480 --> 00:40:32.550
Thirty.

00:40:48.840 --> 00:40:49.710
Mr. ye,

00:40:50.110 --> 00:40:51.070
do you admit your fault?

00:40:58.110 --> 00:40:59.400
You did this to get back at me

00:40:59.630 --> 00:41:00.320
for what I said

00:41:00.320 --> 00:41:01.440
at Lin Xianzhong's house, didn't you?

00:41:02.360 --> 00:41:03.880
That's why you made me a companion

00:41:04.070 --> 00:41:04.880
in the East Palace.

00:41:11.070 --> 00:41:13.070
You're really petty.

00:41:14.760 --> 00:41:16.190
How about another thirty strikes?

00:41:18.070 --> 00:41:18.880
I admit my fault.

00:41:23.110 --> 00:41:24.550
What you have taught me today,

00:41:26.030 --> 00:41:27.150
I dare not forget.

00:41:30.960 --> 00:41:31.670
Your Highness,

00:41:32.000 --> 00:41:33.320
it's getting late.

00:41:33.550 --> 00:41:34.550
Please go rest

00:41:35.230 --> 00:41:37.110
after you catch up on your studies.

00:41:38.880 --> 00:41:39.510
Your servant

00:41:40.070 --> 00:41:40.840
takes leave.

00:41:50.480 --> 00:41:52.190
You're strict with the Crown Prince,

00:41:52.550 --> 00:41:53.840
but rarely resorts to physical punishment.

00:41:54.630 --> 00:41:56.230
Why the strikes today?

00:41:56.710 --> 00:41:58.400
Ye Xian has been in the palace less than three days,

00:41:58.590 --> 00:41:59.760
yet the Crown Prince's tricks

00:41:59.760 --> 00:42:00.920
are already evolving.

00:42:01.400 --> 00:42:02.550
Without a few strikes,

00:42:02.630 --> 00:42:03.710
he wouldn't learn the seriousness

00:42:04.440 --> 00:42:06.070
and he'd get more and more out of hand.

00:42:06.920 --> 00:42:07.630
Actually,

00:42:08.710 --> 00:42:10.230
this is also doing Ye Xian a favor.

00:42:12.670 --> 00:42:13.760
Unless I'm mistaken,

00:42:13.760 --> 00:42:15.280
after those thirty strikes,

00:42:16.070 --> 00:42:17.550
Ye Xian will be able to leave tomorrow.

00:42:19.360 --> 00:42:20.030
You're not

00:42:20.030 --> 00:42:21.670
helping Mr. Ye.

00:42:21.840 --> 00:42:23.440
You're helping Miss Gu!

00:42:29.920 --> 00:42:31.440
That Madame Liu is so unbearable.

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:33.030
The first time you meet,

00:42:33.030 --> 00:42:34.550
she grabbed your hand and wouldn't let go,

00:42:35.000 --> 00:42:37.760
keeping going on about figure, eyes, brows, something like that.

00:42:38.510 --> 00:42:40.280
Looked like she wanted to touch you already!

00:42:41.110 --> 00:42:41.960
She's nothing like

00:42:42.230 --> 00:42:43.920
the sister of the Marchioness.

00:42:44.630 --> 00:42:45.960
She's just like a slave trader!

00:42:47.320 --> 00:42:48.800
Who's tired of living,

00:42:49.030 --> 00:42:50.360
daring to badmouth the marquisate?

00:42:53.360 --> 00:42:54.510
Sir.

00:42:59.960 --> 00:43:01.150
It's just my foolish rambling.

00:43:01.440 --> 00:43:02.630
Please forgive me, sir.

00:43:03.710 --> 00:43:04.440
Get up.

00:43:05.230 --> 00:43:06.280
How did you get in?

00:43:06.710 --> 00:43:07.840
Why was there no announcement?

00:43:09.480 --> 00:43:10.670
I haven't seen you in days,

00:43:10.880 --> 00:43:12.030
yet you've grown bold,

00:43:12.320 --> 00:43:13.440
talking to me like this.

00:43:14.590 --> 00:43:15.920
I heard you're grounded.

00:43:16.590 --> 00:43:17.760
No bother announcing.

00:43:18.070 --> 00:43:19.110
I just climbed the wall.

00:43:21.110 --> 00:43:23.030
Qingpu, go outside and keep watch.

00:43:23.710 --> 00:43:24.840
Yes, Miss.

00:43:31.840 --> 00:43:32.880
What are you waiting for?

00:43:33.360 --> 00:43:34.440
Serve me some tea.

00:44:02.400 --> 00:44:03.360
What tea is this?

00:44:03.800 --> 00:44:05.000
Smells bad already.

00:44:06.480 --> 00:44:07.110
Never mind.

00:44:08.030 --> 00:44:09.000
Back to business.

00:44:10.190 --> 00:44:11.510
You don't want to marry into the Liu family?

00:44:12.070 --> 00:44:12.590
No.

00:44:13.480 --> 00:44:15.110
If my father insists,

00:44:15.630 --> 00:44:17.230
even if I have to make a scene,

00:44:17.630 --> 00:44:18.760
I'll do it to refuse.

00:44:20.110 --> 00:44:21.480
Always making a scene.

00:44:22.230 --> 00:44:22.760
You really

00:44:22.760 --> 00:44:24.190
don't care about your own face.

00:44:24.800 --> 00:44:26.190
For a woman,

00:44:26.440 --> 00:44:27.590
marriage is a lifetime matter.

00:44:27.710 --> 00:44:28.590
What is face

00:44:29.030 --> 00:44:30.000
compared to that?

00:44:31.110 --> 00:44:32.110
Look at you.

00:44:32.590 --> 00:44:33.630
All you've got left

00:44:34.590 --> 00:44:35.920
is this pretty face.

00:44:36.510 --> 00:44:37.800
Otherwise, with your terrible attitude,

00:44:38.030 --> 00:44:39.280
who would dare to marry you?